  VALUES
    (v_mod_id, 4, 'Your path to blog income', E'# Your Path to Blog Income\n\n## 🎓 Congratulations!\n\nYou now have a complete roadmap to building a blog writing business.\n\n## What You''ve Learned\n\n✅ Why businesses pay for blogs\n✅ How to choose profitable niches\n✅ Writing blogs that get results\n✅ Pricing your services\n✅ Getting clients through Local-Link\n✅ Scaling beyond solo work\n\n## Your 30-Day Action Plan\n\n### Week 1\n- Complete your partner profile\n- Create 3 portfolio samples\n- Set your pricing\n\n### Week 2\n- Apply to 10 Local-Link jobs\n- Send 10 outreach emails\n- Land your first client\n\n### Week 3\n- Deliver exceptional work\n- Ask for testimonial\n- Apply to 10 more jobs\n\n### Week 4\n- Land 2-3 more clients\n- Set up batching system\n- Plan for $2,000/month\n\n## Income Milestones\n\n**Month 1-2:** $500-1,000 (2-3 clients)\n**Month 3-4:** $1,500-2,500 (4-6 clients)\n**Month 5-6:** $3,000-5,000 (8-10 clients)\n**Month 7-12:** $5,000-8,000 (scale or hire)\n\n## The Local-Link Advantage\n\nYou''re not building this alone.\n\n- Built-in client demand\n- Certified training\n- Marketplace support\n- Partner community\n\n## Next Steps\n\n1. **Complete your certification exam**\n2. **Build your portfolio** (even if unpaid at first)\n3. **Apply to your first 10 jobs**\n4. **Land your first paying client**\n5. **Deliver amazing work**\n6. **Rinse and repeat**\n\n## Final Thought\n\nThousands of local businesses need what you now know how to do.\n\nThey''ll pay you well for it.\n\nAll you have to do is start.\n\n**Go make it happen. 🚀**\n\n---\n\n## Need Help?\n\n- Join the Local-Link partner community\n- Connect with other blog partners\n- Get ongoing training and support\n\n**Welcome to the Local-Link Partner Family!**', 15)
  ON CONFLICT (module_id, lesson_index) DO UPDATE SET
